\n<Minato Neon>No... I don't have any business in the lesson
room.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (I think it's rude to do this at this
time, but it's okay to talk a little, right...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (No... Maybe I'm overthinking it...
\N[5]-san wouldn't get angry over something like
this, and besides...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (Yes... \N[5]-san always gives me the
words I need the most.)

Previously Translated Text: \N[5]-san... has
always been like that. Whenever we faced any
problems, he would always smile and listen to our
concerns, guiding us in the direction that felt
right.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (I may be clueless when it comes to
romance... sigh... I've been putting in quite a
bit of effort to get noticed though...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (Hmm... I'm starting to get a little
angry.)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (Alright, even if you were sleeping, who
cares! You're the manager, right? It's only
natural for you to take care of my mental well-
being!)

I approached the door with a step, filled with my
pent-up frustration.
I heard it faintly, and my whole body stiffened.
\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] ...Huh!? Wha...

I heard a seductive moan from a woman. As if the
waves were receding from my stiffened body, my
strength began to fade away.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (Wait, is this a lie... \N[5]-san...?
Huh? N-No, no way... hold on a sec...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (First of all... there shouldn't be any
other women in the mansion right now. I haven't
confirmed it for sure, but at least I haven't met
anyone.)
\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (But... beyond this door... no, wait...)
\F[\V[2]]... Suddenly, I feel a sense of déjà vu.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (That's right... It doesn't necessarily
mean there's a woman. There's a possibility that
\N[5]-san is watching the same footage that I've
seen multiple times right now...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (Actually, that possibility seems more
likely. Even if there were other women besides me,
I don't think he would be the kind of person to
bring a woman in at a time like this...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (If that's the case, it might be
impossible now. It would be awkward for both of
us...)

I lowered my arm that was about to knock and took
a step back.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (I wonder what this misunderstanding
is... I just... wanted to meet and talk...)

I turned on my heel and left his room. Come to
think of it, that's always how it's been between
us. We never really connect at crucial moments and
there's always a certain distance between us.

Due to work-related reasons, it can't be helped...
But today, I couldn't help but feel a tug at my
heart as I stopped and looked back.

\#I wait... It's just selfish and self-centered
expectations. \#... But of course, the door to his
room doesn't open as expected, and my faint hopes
are shattered----...

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]...(It's already empty.)

......It seems that the old key is not meant to
open this door.
......It seems that the door is locked.
......It seems that the door is locked.
